    <item>
      <title>Cantor 的 Lutnick 预计 9 月份将降息，2025 年将降息两次</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-31/cantor-s-lutnick-expects-september-rate-cut-two-in-2025</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Cantor Fitzgerald 董事长兼 BGC 集团首席执行官 Howard Lutnick 在接受“彭博未平仓合约”采访时表示，市场认为美联储 9 月份降息的可能性为 100%。（来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-31/cantor-s-lutnick-expects-september-rate-cut-two-in-2025</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 13:45:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>布拉德预计美联储将在 9 月开始降息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-31/bullard-expects-fed-to-start-cutting-rates-in-september-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[前圣路易斯联邦储备银行行长吉姆·布拉德预计美联储将在 9 月份开始降息。他正在接受“彭博监测”采访。（来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-31/bullard-expects-fed-to-start-cutting-rates-in-september-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 13:41:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>波音公司任命凯利·奥特伯格为新任首席执行官</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-31/boeing-names-kelly-ortberg-as-new-ceo</link>
      <description><![CDATA[波音公司任命凯利·奥特伯格为新任首席执行官。这位 64 岁的工程师来自罗克韦尔柯林斯公司，将于 8 月 8 日上任。波音公司股价上涨，因为投资者对现任首席执行官戴夫·卡尔霍恩 3 月宣布辞职后数月的不确定性结束表示欢迎。“彭博社监视”报道了突发新闻。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-31/boeing-names-kelly-ortberg-as-new-ceo</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 13:33:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>微软业绩下滑后，Meta 投资者将重点关注资本支出</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/meta-investors-have-laser-focus-on-capex-after-microsoft-letdown</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Meta Platforms Inc. 的投资者希望它能比微软公司和 Alphabet Inc. 更好地说服华尔街，在人工智能方面投入巨额资金是值得的。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/meta-investors-have-laser-focus-on-capex-after-microsoft-letdown</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 11:12:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泰晤士水务转型计划或于今年加速启动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/thames-water-turnaround-regime-may-be-accelerated-to-start-this-year</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰晤士水务公司的重整计划可能会在今年年底前受到监管机构的监督，因为该公司正竞相避开五月份的最后期限，因为届时它将耗尽资金。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/thames-water-turnaround-regime-may-be-accelerated-to-start-this-year</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 10:58:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>KKR 利润因资产销售改善而飙升，超出预期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/kkr-profit-soars-49-on-improving-asset-sales-beating-estimates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[KKR &amp; Co. 公布第二季度利润超过华尔街预期，因为该收购公司通过出售资产获得的收入超出预期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/kkr-profit-soars-49-on-improving-asset-sales-beating-estimates</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 10:56:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度最大汽车制造商盈利超预期 计划每年推出一款电动汽车</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/maruti-suzuki-beats-profit-forecast-driven-by-surge-in-suv-sales</link>
      <description><![CDATA[玛鲁蒂铃木有限公司公布季度利润好于预期，得益于其运动型多用途车销量增长，该公司计划每年推出一款电动汽车。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/maruti-suzuki-beats-profit-forecast-driven-by-surge-in-suv-sales</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 10:01:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>沙特阿拉伯接近结束持续四个季度的经济衰退</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/saudi-economy-gdp-contracts-for-fourth-quarter-on-opec-oil-curbs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着 OPEC+ 石油减产效应开始减弱，沙特阿拉伯经济萎缩速度有所放缓，但本季度开始可能出现好转，结束自一年前开始的连续下滑趋势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/saudi-economy-gdp-contracts-for-fourth-quarter-on-opec-oil-curbs</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 06:19:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
